data.value: If you are seeing this, well I am sorry to be the bearer of bad news. Your computer has been infected and you've been chosen as the one to pay the price, or well, negotiate with us. But not all hope is lost, you may recover your files by either paying the price, or negotiating with us on the Discord link below. The price is 25$ in Ethereum. ETH : Discord :
